      unfolding HandlePublishResponse_Quorum by (auto simp add: msgTermVersion_def)
    with hyp1 show ?thesis by (meson finite.insertI finite_subset)
  qed auto
  thus ?thesis by (auto simp add: FiniteTermVersions_def)
